因失声而不得不<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/example-dropped-out-of-manchester-pride-after-losing-his-voice-at-creamfields-3031844">取消在曼彻斯特骄傲节的演出</a>。他在社交媒体上说：“我什至不会唱歌。所以今晚我不会在曼彻斯特骄傲节上表演，但祝你度过愉快的时光。”</p><p>去年 6 月，Example 发行了他的第七张录音室专辑《We May Grow Old But We Never Grow Up》，其中收录了<a href="/artists/jme">《JME》</a> 、 <a href="/artists/what-so-not">《What So Not</a> 》等专辑的特色内容。</p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/example-announces-uk-and-ireland-dates-for-huge-bangers-hits-and-a-couple-new-bits-february-2024-tour-3492876">“示例宣布 2024 年英国和爱尔兰大型巡演”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 SAG-AFTRA 投票反对视频游戏发行商https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sag-aftra-holds-vote-to-strike-against-video-game-publishers-3492899?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sag-aftra-holds-投票罢工反对视频游戏发行商Imogen DonovanMon, 04 Sep 2023 11:49:57 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3492899 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="好莱坞作家罢工纠察队标语" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>动视、Insomniac Games 和华纳兄弟游戏被命名</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sag-aftra-holds-vote-to-strike-against-video-game-publishers-3492899">SAG-AFTRA 投票反对视频游戏发行商的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="好莱坞作家罢工纠察队标语" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/actors-writers-stike-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>美国演员工会和美国电视广播艺术家联合会的工会 SAG-AFTRA 宣布打算授权对主要游戏发行商进行罢工。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/stalker-2-heart-of-chornobyl-preview-hands-on-3488629">《潜行者 2：切尔诺贝利之心》预览：残酷，但前景令人难以置信</a></strong></li></ul><p>自7月以来，美国工会成员对该组织与电影电视制片人联盟（AMPTP）之间未能达成协议表示不满。流媒体对演员和工作人员剩余费用的影响以及继续使用人工智能来复制演员的肖像等问题也是争论的焦点。</p><p> 9 月 1 日，SAG-AFTRA <a href="https://www.sagaftra.org/sag-aftra-national-board-votes-unanimously-send-interactive-media-video-game-strike-authorization" target="_blank" rel="noopener">宣布已就互动媒体协议的重新谈判向成员发出罢工授权投票</a>。该工会表示，公司“未能”对“SAG-AFTRA 成员所需的关键条款”做出充分反应，不过讨论将于 9 月 26 日恢复。</p><p>公告中提到的公司包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision">Activision</a> Productions Inc.、Blindlight LLC、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">Disney</a> Character Voices Inc.、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/electronic-arts">Electronic Arts</a> Productions Inc.、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/epic-games">Epic Games</a> , Inc.、Formosa Interactive LLC、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/insomniac-games">Insomniac Games</a> Inc.、Take 2 Productions Inc.、VoiceWorks Productions Inc. 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/wb-games">WB Games</a> Inc. </p><figure id="attachment_3447751" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3447751" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3447751" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spider-man-2@2000x1270.jpg" alt="漫威蜘蛛侠 2" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spider-man-2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spider-man-2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spider-man-2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spider-man-2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spider-man-2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/spider-man-2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3447751" class="wp-caption-text">漫威蜘蛛侠 2。图片来源：Insomniac Games</figcaption></figure><p> “我们再次面临雇主的贪婪和不尊重。人工智能再次使我们的会员面临工作机会减少的危险。 SAG-AFTRA 再次代表其成员对抗暴政。”SAG-AFTRA 主席 Fran Drescher 说道。</p><p> “除了人工智能保护之外，SAG-AFTRA 还寻求为视频游戏表演者提供与电影和电视合同下工作人员相同的工资增长：追溯至到期日加薪 11%，并在第二年和第三年加薪 4%。该协议是会员工资跟上通货膨胀所必需的，”工会表示。</p><p>此外，镜头前的表演者必须有权享受每小时五分钟的休息时间，而镜头外的表演者目前也可以从中受益。除此之外，SAG-AFTRA 强调在进行特技或危险工作时需要有固定医务人员在场。</p><p>应禁止自录试镜的特技，并应在视频游戏行业引入适当的声音压力保护措施。 </p><figure id="attachment_3487366" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3487366" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3487366" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-open-combat-missions.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-open-combat-missions.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-open-combat-missions-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-open-combat-missions-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-open-combat-missions-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-open-combat-missions-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/modern-warfare-3-open-combat-missions-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3487366" class="wp-caption-text"> 《使命召唤：现代战争 3》图片来源：动视</figcaption></figure><p>需要澄清的是，罢工授权并不意味着将会发生罢工。相反，SAG-AFTRA 可以根据月底的讨论结果来选择使用该选项。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/starfield"><em>Starfield</em></a>模组制作者已将<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/seinfeld"><em>《宋飞</em></a>正传》的乔治·科斯坦萨、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-gosling">瑞恩·高斯林</a>和约翰·塞纳添加到科幻游戏中作为可玩角色。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sag-aftra-holds-vote-to-strike-against-video-game-publishers-3492899">SAG-AFTRA 投票反对视频游戏发行商的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
